#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.desktop.in:3
msgid "A simple meditation timer and log"
msgstr "Un minuteur et journal de méditation simple"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.desktop.in:9
msgid "meditation;timer;mindfulness;"
msgstr "méditation;minuteur;pleine conscience;meditation;mindfulness;"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:8
msgid "Meditation timer and session log"
msgstr "Minuteur de méditation et journal de séances"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid ""
"Meditate is a simple meditation companion for GNOME. It provides a countdown "
"and stopwatch timer, a session log, and statistics to help you build a "
"consistent practice."
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:17
msgid "Countdown and stopwatch timer modes"
msgstr "Modes compte à rebours et chronomètre"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:18
msgid "Label your sessions (sitting, walking, chanting, …)"
msgstr "Étiquetez vos séances (assis, en marche, chant, …)"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:19
msgid "Add notes to each session"
msgstr "Ajoutez des notes à chaque séance"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:20
msgid "View your history and statistics"
msgstr "Consultez votre historique et vos statistiques"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:21
msgid "Track your streak and stay consistent"
msgstr "Suivez votre série et gardez le cap"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:28
msgid "Countdown timer with quick presets and streak display"
msgstr "Compte à rebours avec préréglages et série affichée"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:32
msgid "Weekly goal, 13-week heatmap, and insights"
msgstr "Objectif hebdomadaire, heatmap sur 13 semaines et analyses"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:36
msgid "Session log grouped by date, with labels and notes"
msgstr "Journal des séances groupé par date, avec étiquettes et notes"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:52
msgid "janekbt"
msgstr "janekbt"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:105
msgid ""
"Major polish release ahead of Flathub submission — every tab redesigned, new "
"data features, and translations in nine languages."
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:107
msgid "Timer, Stats, and Log tabs fully redesigned around the GNOME HIG"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:108
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Stats now shows a weekly-goal ring, a 13-week contribution heatmap, and an "
"insights panel"
msgstr "Objectif hebdomadaire, heatmap sur 13 semaines et analyses"

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:109
msgid "Log is a date-grouped card feed with swipe-to-delete and undo"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:110
msgid "CSV import and export, plus one-click migration from Insight Timer"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:111
msgid ""
"Real CC0 recordings replace the three built-in end sounds, with Singing bowl "
"as the new default"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:112
msgid "Post-session note field is now multi-line"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:113
msgid "Weekly goal resets on the locale's first day of the week"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:114
msgid "New \"Vibrate on session end\" toggle for Linux phones"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:115
msgid ""
"Full translation coverage across English, German, Spanish, French, Italian, "
"Dutch, Polish, Brazilian Portuguese, Russian, and Simplified Chinese"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:116
msgid ""
"Adaptive layout down to 360 px; HIG-compliant accent colours and "
"accessibility"
msgstr ""

#: data/io.github.janekbt.Meditate.metainfo.xml.in:122
msgid "Initial release."
msgstr "Première version."

